        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-762756669" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-762756669" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="762756669">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Momy/">蜜兜</a>
                    <span>2014-01-03</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">作者还是考虑换个营生吧，这口饭不合适你。浪费了时间才知道原来书名在这儿等着呢！</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="737590109">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-737590109" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-737590109" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="737590109">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/fudatou/">傅踢踢</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2013-10-21</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">雷同的城市，类似的生活，各人自有各人磨的背后，是相近的麻木与孤独。私下揣测，失败者之歌有两重意思，一是个体在时代奔流中生发的无力与荒谬感，二是人性的微光洒落的零星温暖。前者记录了普遍的失败，后者见证了晦暗中仍有拍手作歌。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="461435466">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-461435466" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-461435466" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="461435466">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/tuiblio/">不流</a>
                    <span>2012-01-27</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">往往微就是妙的前提，得小，得细，得碎，才能进入缝隙、深入内部，凡大的都要被阻隔在外部，粗大的线条构成生活的轮廓和线索，而生活的细部却都是相似的失意、失败、挫落…真正的失败来源于情感。。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="862241664">
